::Kaiser::
       He grunts as the shots hit him squarely in his fortified back.  
Growling, he throws his guns slightly above his head and, rising to his feet 
in the process he spins throwing his scimitars at Perceptor.  He then reaches 
over his shoulders and catches his blasters launching another pair of shots 
at Perceptor.
